    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Bundling is the process of combining multiple JavaScript, CSS, and other files into a single file to reduce the number of HTTP requests."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Why Bundling Matters"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Each HTTP request adds overhead. Bundling reduces requests, speeds up loading, and improves performance."
